Package org.jruyi.timeoutadmin

JRuyi Timeout Admin Package Version 1.0

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ITimeoutAdmin
    Service for creating notifiers.
    ITimeoutEvent
    An event indicating that the time is out.
    ITimeoutListener
    This interface defines a callback method for being called on timeout events.
    ITimeoutNotifier
    A ITimeoutNotifier is used to schedule a timeout notification of the interested subject.
